snippet.title: Red Siren: Space Defense
snippet.description:
Red Siren: Space Defense is coming on 8th November 2018.

Get ready to play one of the most action packed games ever!

Red Siren is a unique arcade shooter with constant, high-paced and greatly rewarding action. Enjoy the gorgeous, full 3D visuals while you crush all the countless enemies! Complete missions with flying colors and pimp your starfighter to the maximum, or even further!

The game is scheduled to be released on 8th November 2018 on iOS and Android for FREE!
